{"tid":2486293,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個已經冇人講嘅生鬼廣東話諺語","createTime":"2021-04-12T20:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T12:19:55.000Z","uid":289257,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4da96c14bcdc1e7a529b4cdbb1226b5bafef3a","tid":2486293,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:36:25.000Z","msg":"船頭尺<br />\n失匙夾萬<br />\n口爽荷包立<br />\n馬地落地行<br />\n冇雷公咁遠<br />\n畫公仔畫出腸<br />\n雞腸<br />\n絞腸沙<br />\n生仔唔知仔心肝<br />\n好仔不論爺田地，好女唔論嫁妝衣<br />\n蒙頭入閘<br />\n冤豬頭都有聞鼻菩薩<br />\n泥菩薩過江<br />\n觀音頭掃把腳<br />\n上面蒸鬆糕，下面賣涼粉<br />\n阿茂整餅<br />\n火燒旗杆<br />\n長崎涼美<br />\n東急阿雪<br />\n平治煞車器/Ben屎咇嚦<br />\n唔賭唔知時運高，唔嫖唔知身體好<br />\n金魚佬<br />\n含吹奶啜磨拎fing <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重有冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8156994b06c630d7dcfbf540b67bf8093c9f01","tid":2486293,"uid":129340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:37:54.000Z","msg":"七國咁亂"},{"pid":"c781a3fa01263ab5bb80bfbbe4275446ca976d08","tid":2486293,"uid":129340,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:38:32.000Z","msg":"咪蝦我膝頭哥唔食辣椒醬"},{"pid":"1e7010de209a05a0a6f752f2a8f9c1eee2cbafb1","tid":2486293,"uid":289257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c781a3fa01263ab5bb80bfbbe4275446ca976d08","tid":2486293,"uid":129340,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:38:32.000Z","msg":"咪蝦我膝頭哥唔食辣椒醬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:40:14.000Z","msg":"又係度車大炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7124c992471a160f40eda396e81371f65e9a19d1","tid":2486293,"uid":208323,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T20:40:34.000Z","msg":"呃鬼食豆腐"},{"pid":"cb97148a69af1c7684ebfa3267269ae0dbef6c9d","tid":2486293,"uid":129340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e70