<br />\n上面蒸鬆糕，下面賣涼粉<br />\n阿茂整餅<br />\n火燒旗杆<br />\n長崎涼美<br />\n東急阿雪<br />\n平治煞車器/Ben屎咇嚦<br />\n唔賭唔知時運高，唔嫖唔知身體好<br />\n金魚佬<br />\n含吹奶啜磨拎fing <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNVDnmgdsfdXrph95RSPspcFwLq7z8hvHqw4KUHB4YTJW?filename=Ep10F7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp10F7Q.jpg&h=cdce4913&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdBVijGtXCNFznS5uXwRCBCh82D4YiAC4W5EiuAksABAV?filename=K2ZNk7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2ZNk7Q.jpg&h=94b301e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ9SwLFRb3RcJokwrpFer2zhPu3r4Fn3TfTV7B4MXmqTx?filename=8W9aiUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8W9aiUx.jpg&h=cb903bb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bc85cd4ef4ba979cae3f226c4f2d16ce3289098","tid":2486293,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T22:03:00.000Z","msg":"打刧紅毛鬼 進貢法蘭西"},{"pid":"eb55dbe56436ca546c37b6e53ffb1f9aa792e241","tid":2486293,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db168cca4611b1e30f12ff2779055eb00782d3cb","tid":2486293,"uid":312430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:03:26.000Z","msg":"笑談廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T22:05:11.000Z","msg":"近排真係特別多呢d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81f1035f8fdf17b725b76f626836b1e89fc2c4c","tid":2486293,"uid":97240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"753381bd75527711a1f5a08906d2b948859a2f50","tid":2486293,"uid":312363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:20:43.000Z","msg":"畫公仔畫出腸點會冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T23:04:28.000Z","msg":"蒙頭入閘都係<br />\n樓主00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2